    "---\n",
    "## 🧠 STEP 6: LLM-Powered NLP Alert Summarizer\n",
    "*Core intelligence: LLM analyzes flows and generates human-readable threat reports*"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
